'''Bosse Johansson''' (born 1965) is the [[Chief executive officer|CEO]] at [[Swedbank]] Sjuhärad in [[Borås]]. He also has been a [[Chairman]] of [[IF Elfsborg]] since 2004, where he replaced Sture Svensson after his resignment. He was chosen along with Elfsborg's new Sporting Director Stefan Andreasson.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.svenskelitfotboll.se/sefaktuellt/elfsborg_sep.htm|title=Bosse Johansson nye ordförande för Elfsborg|publisher=svenskelitfotboll.se|accessdate=2012-07-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061230083451/http://www.svenskelitfotboll.se/sefaktuellt/elfsborg_sep.htm|archivedate=2006-12-30|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.elfsborg.se/images/Webbinnehall/verksamhetsberattelser/IFElfsborg_verkshb_2011.pdf|title=Bosse Johansson redovisar Elfsborg verksamhetsberättlse 2011 Elfsborg|publisher=elfsborg.se|accessdate=2012-07-02}}{{dead link|date=July 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

